layout.text: A Better Way to Line Your Tray!

Unique CageCatchers are designed to eliminate unsightly and unsanitary conditions of your bird cages for only pennies. The special hypo-allergenic, treated paper bird cage liners from CageCatchers are designed to allow placing a full week's supply in each bird tray bottom.
